Package bibliothek.gui.dock

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExpandableToolbarItemStrategy
    An ExpandableToolbarItemStrategy is a strategy that allows to expand and to shrink items of a toolbar.
    ToolbarItem
    A ToolbarItem is an item that is shown as part of a toolbar.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractToolbarDockStation
    Base class of a DockStation behaving like a typical toolbar: the children are ordered in a list, an optional title and border may be shown.
    ToolbarContainerDockStation
    A Dockable and a DockStation which stands for a group of ToolbarGroupDockStation.
    ToolbarDockStation
    A Dockable and a DockStation which stands for a group of ToolbarItemDockable.
    ToolbarGroupDockStation
    A Dockable and a DockStation which stands a group of ToolbarDockStation.
    ToolbarItemDockable
    A ToolbarItemDockable is a Dockable that can be shown as child of a ToolbarDockStation.
